# Readex Pro font binaries live here (declared in pubspec.yaml, family ReadexPro).
#
# The four .ttf files in this folder are currently EMPTY PLACEHOLDERS so the
# Flutter asset bundle resolves and the app builds. Replace each with the real
# Readex Pro weight, keeping the same filename:
#   ReadexPro-Regular.ttf  (400)
#   ReadexPro-Medium.ttf   (500)
#   ReadexPro-SemiBold.ttf (600)
#   ReadexPro-Bold.ttf     (700)
# Readex Pro contains BOTH Latin and Arabic glyphs — no separate Arabic face.
